OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,FBrendon McCullum has left his role as
OL,7,FEngland's Test head coach but will
OL,8,Fremain in charge of the white-ball set-
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,FMcCullum has paid the price for a poor
OL,12,Frun of red-ball form with a 4-1 defeat
OL,13,Fin last winter's Ashes followed by a 2-
OL,14,F1 home loss to New Zealand last month,
OL,15,Fwhich occurred against the backdrop of
OL,16,Fanother off-the-field incident under
OL,17,Fthe watch of the Kiwi coach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
