OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,FBen Stokes announced his international
OL,7,Fretirement midway through defeat at
OL,8,FTrent Bridge, and that will prove the
OL,9,Ffinal Test of McCullum's England red-
OL,10,Fball tenure.
OL,12,FIt started in extraordinary fashion in
OL,13,F2022 with 'Bazball' taking the cricket
OL,14,Fworld by storm. England's bold and
OL,15,Ffresh attack-minded approach under
OL,16,FMcCullum and Stokes led to 3-0 series
OL,17,Fwins over New Zealand and in Pakistan,
OL,18,Fwhere 500 runs were scored in one day,
OL,19,Fbefore a thrilling 2-2 home Ashes in
OL,20,F2023, but the trajectory soon changed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,FA 4-1 thumping in India two years ago
OL,7,Fexposed England's stubborn and at
OL,8,Ftimes naive mantra and along with
OL,9,Fmultiple disciplinary issues, McCullum
OL,10,Fhas lost his Test role months after
OL,11,Fthe overseas Ashes were lost in 11
OL,12,Fdays during an abject tour of
OL,13,FAustralia.
OL,15,FIt leaves England in need of a new
OL,16,Fhead coach and captain for red-ball
OL,17,Fcricket.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
