PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,FRichard Gould, the England and Wales
OL,7,FCricket Board's chief executive
OL,8,Fofficer, said: "Brendon breathed new
OL,9,Flife into England men's Test team
OL,10,Fduring an exciting period which saw
OL,11,Fsome amazing victories and we're
OL,12,Fgrateful for all he has given to the
OL,13,Frole.
OL,15,F"We now believe that the time is right
OL,16,Fto make a change for the Test team as
OL,17,Fwe target victory in the Ashes next
OL,18,Fsummer."
OL,26,@pD@POUwD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
