PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,F"It's been an absolute privilege to
OL,7,Fwatch him shape the mentality of the
OL,8,Fteam, to one the players have loved
OL,9,Fand see him develop a new generation
OL,10,Fof talent who will be at the heart of
OL,11,FEngland men's teams for years to come.
OL,13,F"He leaves the Test team well-set and
OL,14,Fpoised to achieve great things."
OL,16,FThis news occurred the day after
OL,17,FEngland's T20 team thrashed India by a
OL,18,F56-run margin at Ageas Bowl to seal a
OL,19,F4-0 Vitality Series win under McCullum.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
