PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,FMcCullum, who took on the white-ball
OL,7,Frole in 2024 and will remain in charge
OL,8,Fof the one-day set-up, won 25 of his
OL,9,F44 Tests and said that while he was
OL,10,F"gutted" to leave the Test role, he
OL,11,F"respects" the decision to make a
OL,12,Fchange.
OL,14,F"I've absolutely loved coaching the
OL,15,FTest side and I'm incredibly proud of
OL,16,Fwhat we've achieved together. There've
OL,17,Fbeen some unbelievable highs and a few
OL,18,Ftough days along the way, but that's
OL,19,Fall part of taking on a challenge like
OL,20,Fthis," he said.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@HO]sD@AOUsD@JO]vD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
