OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,F"It's been a privilege and an honour,
OL,7,Fand I'm grateful. Grateful to the
OL,8,Fplayers, the staff and the fans who
OL,9,Fsupported us on the journey.
OL,11,F"Of course I'm gutted not to be
OL,12,Fcontinuing, but I respect the
OL,13,Fdecision. My focus now is on giving
OL,14,Feverything I've got to the white-ball
OL,15,Fteams and helping England keep moving
OL,16,Fforward.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
