PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,F"I wish the Test team nothing but
OL,7,Fsuccess. There's a hell of a lot of
OL,8,Ftalent in that dressing room and
OL,9,Fthey're a special bunch of lads.
OL,11,F"I'll always be backing the boys, with
OL,12,Fa smile on my face, and hoping they
OL,13,Fkeep taking the game on. I know
OL,14,Fthey'll continue to make people proud."
OL,16,FFormer Australia captains Justin
OL,17,FLanger and Ricky Ponting have both
OL,18,Fbeen touted for as possible England
OL,19,Fcoaches in the past, while a second
OL,20,Fstint at the helm for Zimbabwean Andy
OL,21,FFlower would also be a popular option.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
