PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783902027
OL,3,CMcCullum 'gutted' as he's sacked as
OL,4,CEngland Test cricket coach
OL,6,FAndrew Flintoff has also been spoken
OL,7,Fof as a future England coach by Key,
OL,8,Fwho is a close friend, and he is
OL,9,Feffectively an internal candidate due
OL,10,Fto his role in charge of the England
OL,11,FLions setup. Whether he has the
OL,12,Fexperience to oversee a rebuild of the
OL,13,FTest regime is less clear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
